{"tid":1902160,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我屌哂你哋老母！！！","createTime":"2020-02-28T07:59:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T15:34:36.000Z","uid":163207,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e4d7a360ea29484a7f6f3126146ba14257ae11a1","tid":1902160,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:59:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我屌哂你哋老母！</span></span><br />\n係咪建立咗城邦 永續基本法達到左啦？ 做咩成個熱門都係食玩膠同睇女post？<br />\n<br />\n如果呢個post上唔到<span style=\"color: gold;\">熱門</span> 冇哂陳雲post 我正式宣布呢個香港真係玩完 連登已死 連我個<span style=\"color: blue;\">淺藍老母</span>都問啲城邦派係咪搞完事 國師同特朗普直deal外國戰線著哂火咁大粒核彈都冇人理既？<br />\n<br />\n應承我 唔好當國師係condom 我哋要奶佢個春袋 呢粒核彈會令到中共好驚 城邦會戰勝歸來 千祈唔可以中販民分化撚嘅計 推走熱門行動Post 唔係我哋就嚟輸<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最後 <br />\n陳雲受痛苦 被人當正柒頭<br />\n至高寶訓 盡見於國師的手<br />\n城邦見！</span></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e69c6eac3ebeae481ca180827c97f8b6866034ac","tid":1902160,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:12:36.000Z","msg":"樓主屌得好"},{"pid":"9bf3e2f8b55f87805977788ef9e1c3abad918872","tid":1902160,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e69c6eac3ebeae481ca180827c97f8b6866034ac","tid":1902160,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:12:36.000Z","msg":"樓主屌得好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:13:23.000Z","msg":"未轉ACC喔你"},{"pid":"8e9cd00c18769f52c7f4a6fbb5b2bc609ce3a44a","tid":1902160,"uid":236414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:13:52.000Z","msg":"我屌哂你哋老母 係咪光復左香港 五大訴求達到左啦？ <br />\n做咩成個熱門都係食玩膠同睇女post？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>如果呢個post上唔到熱門 冇哂行動post 我正式宣布呢個運動真係玩完 連登已死 </ins></span><br />\